ow (which wasn't anywhere CLOSE to extraordinary prior) by making the zone tedious and predictable.  I had to abandon one of my preferred experience spots because this untolerable crack patch just plain SUCKS.<br><br>   I can fully understand why my friends and guild mates are leaving the game in droves - not from the Grey of course - but from every single zone becoming a cookie cutter image of it.  I won't even go into the other reasons, everyone knows them.  Which is sad if you think about it; I bet you could name me at least ten, fifty, or 100 solid reasons to delete this game from your hard drive forever.<br><br>     <p>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=171494</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uligge.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ligge</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/31/02 3:32:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=27474.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.eqguide.com/changingtide/images/ligsmall.jpg width=100 height=129></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Grey... sigh</span><hr size=1> See the rant section.<br><br>This is a bug and is probably fix Wednesday. <p><p align=left><font face="Trebuchet MS, Tahoma" size="1"><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=81719>Ligge</a> - Changing Tide Tyrant<br><font color=green><a href="http://pub17.ezboard.com/beqguide">Changing Tide's Boards</a><b> || </b><a href="http://pub2.ezboard.com/bthefolk">The Folk's Boards</a></font><br>"You must do the thing you think you cannot do." - Eleanor Roosevelt </font></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title>